typewriter_SAPIENT -e takes similar training time with baselines as it collects all the trajectories from MCTS and do not incur additional search cost.
Even with \method, the training time is only about 2 times longer than baselines. This is because conversation simulation only requires forward propagation without gradient backward, so even conducting 20 rollouts per user will not significantly reduce efficiency.
Also note that during inference, the efficiency of \methodis comparable with baselines, as tree search is not required during inference.
